  <body>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> includes a document template to help you get started with JSON
      documents. The template is called <uicontrol>JSON</uicontrol> and it can be found in the
        <uicontrol>New Document</uicontrol> folder in the <xref
        href="new-dialog-sa.dita#new-dialog-sa" product="developer editor"
          ><uicontrol>New</uicontrol> document wizard</xref><xref
        href="creating-from-templates.dita#creating-from-templates"
        product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><uicontrol>New from templates</uicontrol>
        wizard</xref>.</p>
    <p>This section explains the features of the <ph keyref="product"/> JSON Editor and how to use
      them.</p>
